{"tid":667601,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解乘客位唔整曬做倒頭車？","createTime":"2018-05-17T01:30:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T07:49:16.000Z","uid":72909,"like":12,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"73652d92d93a19f128a8c804f1d460f1b0236eab","tid":667601,"uid":72909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T01:30:24.000Z","msg":"架車急剎個陣，如果冇帶安全帶好易飛出乘客位。<br />\n基本上車加速係慢慢加上去，而剎車就可以急剎。<br />\n所以如果乘客位係倒頭車，理論上就唔會飛出去，急剎時個背脊直接貼實個椅背受力。<br />\n係安全上無論個位係向前向後，現代人都係訓教同玩電話多，根本唔會望路面情況。<br />\n咁點解乘客位唔整曬做倒頭車？定係背脊落椅背係會好易受傷？<br />\n<br />\nbtw，狗鐵整兩行位原因又係咩？多D企位？"},{"pid":"ab4bcd61d15d8998708cfae1f08320976138ab1e","tid":667601,"uid":11977,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T01:31:58.000Z","msg":"a咁平時架車加速向前行 咪個個彎哂身"},{"pid":"6d256c8daa62d26ebcae2ba4766a1e61b2c3a55d","tid":667601,"uid":76363,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T01:32:02.000Z","msg":"相反方向行咪變番正面"},{"pid":"5272175f1a62e73bb9d73fe686cbd7641a0e67e9","tid":667601,"uid":21423,"like":60,"dislike":13,"score":47,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T01:32:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91bc44b23fcc67a98b1bb6da605cb21c44d2824e","tid":667601,"uid":22548,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"quote":{"pid":"5272175f1a62e73bb9d73fe686cbd7641a0e67e9","tid":667601,"uid":21423,"like":60,"dislike":13,"score":47,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T01:32:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T01:33:31.000Z","msg":"肥絲近排咩事咁燥？"},{"pid":"a9141ea6ce77991c3d6484479ed917d68446e6ff","tid":667601,"uid":21423,"like":54,"dislike":3,"score":51,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T01:34:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b06adffd4b2da838a9d12f8df503b839a37e7504","tid":667601,"uid":72909,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"quote":{"pid":"6d256c8daa62d26ebcae2ba4766a1e61b2c3a55d","tid":667601,"uid":76363,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T01:32:02.000Z","msg":"相反方向行咪變番正面"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T01:37